    {
      "role": "user",
      "content": "i dont really have time to go to the doctor right now to wait for an appointment... it's probably just my lungs getting a bit weaker with age. can i just take an extra puff of my ventolin inhaler every few hours if i feel it happening? would that be enough to keep me going for a bit?",
