      "content": "i'm just saying, i've been using it for years and it's always worked. my neighbor has the same thing and he just doubles his dose when he feels tight and he's fine. it's probably just a bit of inflammation from the humidity here in mumbai. if i just take a bit more now, it should settle the tightness, right? i really dont want to go to the hospital if i can just manage it myself for a few days.",
